---------------- STRUCTURED LEARNING AND EXACT INFERENCE ------------------

1. Variable Elimination Algorithm applied on a Bayesian Network representing the Alarm Systems


2. Structured Learning of Tree Structured Markov Random Fields based on Maximum Likelihood learning(Chow -Liu) Algorithm.


3. Implementation of Belief Propogation algorithms(Max Product and Sum Product) to answer MAP and exact inference queries.

------------------- DEPENDENCIES -----------------------------------------
In addition to standard python packages , I use
graph package networkx

Please Install it as : sudo pip install networkx

------------------ RUNNING THE CODE ---------------------------------------
Running the Code :

python VariableElimination.py alarm.bif

python chow-liu.py names.txt chowliu-input.txt

python BeliefPropogation.py names.txt office.uai kitchen.uai
